{"tid":1779305,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【國際專家小組請辭】Ben Sir王喜齊嘲監警會","createTime":"2019-12-11T14:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T14:41:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1f669c8ab2ff774088cfa1aca29009859d54d2","tid":1779305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_713390_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_713390_0&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAG1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=d07ef1a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_713390_0&h=fb42731b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_713390_0</a><br />\n<br />\n【國際專家小組請辭】Ben Sir王喜齊嘲監警會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20191211/1536pix/1576059810_29bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20191211%2F1536pix%2F1576059810_29bb.png&h=b364389e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正當好多香港人都知，監警會幾咁有能力「監警」，但偏偏喜歡執意而行嘅阿娥，堅持監警會做到監察警隊作用。<br />\n<br />\n今日《華爾街日報》報道，監警會國際專家小組成員已請辭，連專家小組發表官方聲明，亦表明因監警會無權力進行調查同搜證，故決定退出(formally stand aside from its role)。<br />\n<br />\n講到咁，但監警會主市梁定邦同副主席謝偉銓，就否認專家小組集體辭職，辨稱佢哋只係工作「告一段落」喎！<br />\n<br />\n呢六個月，港人已經喺政府長期「訓練」下，做到你有你自圓其說，我有我自行判斷，時刻頭腦清醒。所以監警會國際專家小組成員已請辭一事上，Ben Sir以妙論表達香港已經幾咁荒謬:「今時今日嘅社會，假如男性海外調查專家突然話畀你聽要離隊生仔，而你都覺得合情合理時，啲高官描述佢哋辭職定早退定唔得閒，又有乜所謂呢？」跟手#男性專家原來去生仔。<br />\n<br />\n而王喜亦忍唔住喺fb留言:「國際調查團隊總辭原因:皇家香港警察，撲滅罪行永垂不朽。私家香港警察，撲滅市民卻無從稽考。」。"},{"pid":"7639aa1409d792732a99d0c83edf3855fe5b877c","tid":1779305,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"努力打好國際線<br />\n今日香港都成為美加焦點<br />\n<br />\n 【Twitter要人!!】美加議員人權日tweet集合list!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要人入去推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}